=\"#feedbackModal_main_3612189\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 07, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bqf1665702639504.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bqf1665702639504.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bqf1665702639504.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bqf1665702639504\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property determines whether the data in the widget is displayed on more than one line, and whether carriage returns can be used when entering data.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Multiline=\"True</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">False\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"bqf1665702639504__table_d12500e1_d12501e1_d12502e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bqf1665702639504__table_d12500e1_d12501e1_d12502e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bqf1665702639504__table_d12500e1_d12501e1_d12502e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bqf1665702639504__table_d12500e1_d12501e1_d12502e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bqf1665702639504__table_d12500e1_d12501e1_d12502e1__entry__2\">The widget can be longer than one line and\n                     carriage returns are allowed.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bqf1665702639504__table_d12500e1_d12501e1_d12502e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bqf1665702639504__table_d12500e1_d12501e1_d12502e1__entry__2\">The widget is a single line.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bqf1665702639504__section_dwz_hbd_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d594762e104\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"bqf1665702639504__table_d11987e1_d11988e1_d11989e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bqf1665702639504__section_qjc_kbd_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d594762e150\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bqf1665702639504__p_d105875e1_d105876e1_d105877e1\">Vertical or horizontal scroll bars are displayed\n            for a multiline widgets only if the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Vertical Scroll Bar</span> and\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Horizontal Scroll Bar</span> properties are selected</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bqf1665702639504__p_d105878e1_d105879e1_d105880e1\">When <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Multiline</span> is\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, the user can enter carriage returns. However, to have data\n            automatically wrap to the next line, the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Automatic Word Wrap</span>\n            property must also be <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bqf1665702639504__p_d105881e1_d105882e1_d105883e1\">The No Display (NDI) syntax definition is not\n            supported in a multiline widgets.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bqf1665702639504__section_vdd_lbd_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d594762e183\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bqf1665702639504__p_d105887e1_d105888e1_d105889e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Multiline</span> property is\n            not dynamic, and can only be set in ProcScript before the form is displayed (for\n            example, by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">display</span> statement in the\n            exec operation). For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"bqf1665702639504__pre_iwr_mbd_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation exec\n $properties(FLD1) = \"multiline=false\"\n edit\nend; exec</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bqf1665702639504__section_ahg_4bd_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d594762e205\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"bqf1665702639504__ul_fcv_4bd_zwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bqf1665702639504__li_d42032e1_d42033e1_d42034e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"klb1688454363706.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/klb1688454363706.html\" title=\"Default logical widget for entering and displaying data in a field in a Form or Report.\">EditBox</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bqf1665702639504__li_d42035e1_d42036e1_d42037e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qwk1688451210612.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qwk1688451210612.html\" title=\"The urtfeditbox widget is used to display and edit text as Rich Text Format (RTF), which supports formatting such as font and color attributes, text alignment, indentation, and lists. Uniface provides a logical widget called RichEditBox, which is mapped to urtfeditbox.\">urtfeditbox (RichEditBox)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612189\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612189\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Multiline Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 07, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 This property determines whether the data in the widget is displayed on more than one line, and whether carriage returns can be used when entering data. Multiline=\"True | False\" Value Description True The widget can be longer than one line and carriage returns are allowed. False The widget is a single line. Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: None Description Vertical or horizontal scroll bars are displayed for a multiline widgets only if the Vertical Scroll Bar and Horizontal Scroll Bar properties are selected When Multiline is True , the user can enter carriage returns. However, to have data automatically wrap to the next line, the Automatic Word Wrap property must also be True . The No Display (NDI) syntax definition is not supported in a multiline widgets. Example: Setting in ProcScript The Multiline property is not dynamic, and can only be set in ProcScript before the form is displayed (for example, by the edit or display statement in the exec operation). For example: operation exec $properties(FLD1) = \"multiline=false\" edit end; exec Copy Applies To EditBox urtfeditbox (RichEditBox) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}